====Division One====
The Africa Division One tournament was played in [[Nairobi]], [[Kenya]], from 1–10 July 2017. [[Kenya national under-19 cricket team|Kenya]] won the tournament on [[net run rate]] from [[Uganda national cricket team|Uganda]] to qualify for their first World Cup since 2002; four African teams will play in the World Cup for the first time since 2006.<ref>[https://www.icc-cricket.com/news/435476 "Kenya stun Uganda to qualify for U19 World Cup 2018"]</ref>
