====Division One====
{{update-section|date=August 2018}}
The Europe Division One tournament will be played in [[Jersey]] from 23 July to 1 August 2017. The four participating teams were [[Denmark national under-19 cricket team|Denmark]], [[Ireland national under-19 cricket team|Ireland]], [[Jersey national under-19 cricket team|Jersey]], and [[Scotland national under-19 cricket team|Scotland]].<ref>[https://www.bbc.com/sport/cricket/38344027 "ICC Under-19 World Cup: Jersey to host European qualifying tournament"], BBC Sport, 16 December 2016. Retrieved 19 December 2016.</ref>

